{"tid":339870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌佢老母讓坐俾支那蝗仲要係幼蟲係咪傻撚咗？","createTime":"2017-07-29T12:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T12:09:39.000Z","uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f21294cfe528d6d7a0f8907ac1a99ba3fe1f5e26","tid":339870,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:08:59.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母讓坐俾支那已經戇鳩<br />\n仲要俾啲嘈怨巴閉嘅幼蟲<br />\n啲人係咪傻鳩咗啊屌佢老母<br />\n<br />\n啱先睇撚住個傻閪啊嬸讓撚完<br />\n隻蟲一句唔該都無就坐撚咗<br />\n蝗蟲死全家啦賤種<br />\n<br />\n不過依啲嘢阻止唔到人<br />\n只可以奉勸大家唔好做依啲缺德行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/95oha6xe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F95oha6xe&h=9377c4b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">隔離個呀伯好似cy</span></span>"},{"pid":"d642aabb8b0c26fce4b15de7f13da95e2e68736a","tid":339870,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}